reviewText:
Rented this one off my Blockbuster At Home.  Talk about pathetic.  It's a good thing it didn't cost anything.  Cheesy, and I guess it was supposed to be a horror/comedy.
The comedy was the acting.  No horror in it.  Unless you want to count the cheap sound effects, and special effects.  Very little blood, or gore. Do yourself a big favor, and skip this one!!!
